      "title": "Demonstration in Maldives to expel Kota from the country",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "A protest is being held in front of the Maldives President's Office demanding the immediate expulsion of Sri Lankan President Gotabaya Rajapaksa from the country."
